{"tid":1826247,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"拯救連登垂死的熱門, 我們要改的幾個習慣","createTime":"2020-01-16T03:21:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-16T09:31:24.000Z","uid":57633,"like":32,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"cec49da52057c3df823bfdaafca0d0f29ec160d5","tid":1826247,"uid":57633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T03:21:13.000Z","msg":"半年來，愈見惡化。議題被網民壞習慣，以及網軍的無形之手操控。<br />\n然後你說：運動靜咗好多。<br />\n改變自己，改變習慣。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">a) 不是正統媒體的新聞，不轉發。<br />\nb) 未經 fact check 的消息，不要理。<br />\nc) 很多文宣大台都是盜取內容，不轉發。<br />\nd) 只轉發原創者的內容。<br />\ne) 貼報道上討論區，只取少量內容，鼓勵點擊。</span><br />\n<br />\n再重覆，目標為上，才可以拯救連登垂死的熱門。<br />\n比方說，<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1) 如果兩日後有遊行，專注推行動 post；<br />\n2) 同一議題，集中處理，不要分散；<br />\n3) 有人留言「拉」，網友不需再留言；<br />\n4) 戒除政治 J 女性癖，不要再討論區議員身材；<br />\n5) 未能 fact check 的事情，忍痛讓佢沉；<br />\n6) 減少用極端字眼，例如「就嚟輸」；<br />\n7) 至為重要：不 要 再 推 假 標 題。</span><br />\n<br />\n議題熱度，講求集中。<br />\n輿論誠信，講求實例。<br />\n網絡生態，講求習慣。<br />\n<br />\n以上說話，難聽，不合耳。其實，我都可以不開口。<br />\n但對於香港人，我有更大信心。改變習慣，重奪輿論主導權，大家一定做得到。<br />\n香港人，改變。<br />\nP.S. 如果覺得有意思，煩請分享，謝謝你。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>原文</strong></ins><br />\n媒體戰爭之中ㅤ我們要改的幾個習慣<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%AA%92%E9%AB%94%E6%88%B0%E7%88%AD%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%AD%E1%85%A0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E8%A6%81%E6%94%B9%E7%9A%84%E5%B9%BE%E5%80%8B%E7%BF%92%E6%85%A3/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25AA%2592%25E9%25AB%2594%25E6%2588%25B0%25E7%2588%25AD%25E4%25B9%258B%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E1%2585%25A0%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2580%2591%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%2594%25B9%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25B9%25BE%25E5%2580%258B%25E7%25BF%2592%25E6%2585%25A3%2F&d=LzGu2J%2BtBqWvyoHzd7Q7GL%2FjevXO%2BySp3REELKrGah4%3D&h=85e96082\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%25AA%2592%25E9%25AB%2594%25E6%2588%25B0%25E7%2588%25AD%25E4%25B9%258B%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E1%2585%25A0%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2580%2591%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%2594%25B9%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25B9%25BE%25E5%2580%258B%25E7%25BF%2592%25E6%2585%25A3%2F&h=68505e0a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%AA%92%E9%AB%94%E6%88%B0%E7%88%AD%E4%B9%8B%E4%B8%AD%E1%85%A0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E8%A6%81%E6%94%B9%E7%9A%84%E5%B9%BE%E5%80%8B%E7%BF%92%E6%85%A3/</a>"},{"pid":"95673f322fd4f70d22065a58551eaed8cf66428e","tid":1826247,"uid":57633,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T03:23:42.000Z","msg":"另外<br />\n仲係好多人比黑警扮朋友呃口供<br />\n<br />\n而且比人拉個時<br />\n你隔離個人都可能係黑警<br />\n唔好以為一齊坐就係自己人<br />\n<br />\n請記住<span style=\"color: red;\">我無野講</span>"},{"pid":"43ff2dd9ada0e06cb65cab740df810b752c0b9f4","tid":1826247,"uid":57633,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T03:28:14.000Z","msg":"推post 除左行動日子<br />\n最好可以順便提埋&quot;我無野講&quot; &quot;FC左先好信&quot;<br />\n<br />\n例子<br />\n<br />\n119 大遊行<br />\n我無野講<br />\n我要見律師<br />\n我要見醫生<br />\nFC左先好信"},{"pid":"f5c5bfab2ac335de229f542aa37158be3310e97b","tid":1826247,"uid":57633,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T03:31:15.000Z","msg":"119 大遊行<br />\n我無野講<br />\n我要見律師<br />\n我要見醫生<br />\nFC左先好信"},{"pid":"f13b9887f6dd1be58ec25f11a00ccf959209ff0f","tid":1826247,"uid":57633,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T03:31:47.000Z","msg":"119 大遊行 遮打見<br />\n我無野講<br />\n我要見律師<br />\n我要見醫生<br />\nFC左先好信"},{"pid":"2302c8e9e7ba59fe272c02f11d92e1cbb0877a5d","tid":1826247,"uid":157938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T03:31:59.000Z","msg":"Up"},{"pid":"0d5f8ebc2163f16486369ccc0c52c7306fd9e418","tid":1826247,"uid":57633,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2302c8e9e7ba59fe272c02f11d92e1cbb0877a5d","tid":1826247,"uid":157938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T03:31:59.000Z","msg":"Up"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T03:33:04.000Z","msg":"試下改你推post習慣<img src=\"/assets/face